description: Sgt. Major is back and his prey for today is a young and beautiful newcomer. Willow has such a look of innocence, that he can't help bu to put his sadistic hands all over her body. She is restrained in steel and is helpless to his evil ways. She is tormented and played with however he pleases, and she has no choice, but to take everything he dishes out.
title: Newcomer Loses Her Innocence
